# Module Scope

When working on a module, only touch the current module and required shared modules.

## Allowed cross-module dependency
- business modules can depend on `mall-common` and `mall-infra`
- `mall-app` can depend on all business modules

## Disallowed behavior
- Do not put user logic into order module
- Do not put cart logic into product module
- Do not put MQ consumer logic into order module
- Do not bypass shared enums / exceptions / result wrappers

## Output expectations
Always provide:
- file paths
- complete imports
- mapper + xml if persistence is required
- explanation of why files are placed in the current module
